Implementation of BLC matrix factorisation recommendation, https://arxiv.org/abs/1509.05789

Supports single and multi-processing plus use of GPU acceleration.

Changelog:
v0.0 Initial commit. NH
v0.1 Added cross-validation. AC
v0.2 Added regular matrix factorisation. 

